Subject: Believe (Dima Bilan album) 
To: Dave
Content:
Believe is the fifth studio album and the debut English language album by Russian singer and songwriter Dima Bilan. It was released in 2009 in Russia and will be released all over Europe during the summer 2009. The album includes his Eurovision Song Contest 2008 winning song "Believe". 
